&lt;/tr>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td>Exquisite Cron Meal&lt;/td>
&lt;td>&lt;strong>MANDATORY&lt;/strong> for any capped NW.&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td>Carolin&amp;rsquo;s Kindness&lt;/td>
&lt;td>Only lasts for 30m, but &lt;strong>VERY&lt;/strong> nice to have.&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;/tbody>
&lt;/table>
